#

Caprese Sandwich

15 min
$6.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

EasyQuickFresh

Description

A fresh and delicious sandwich layered with mozzarella, tomatoes, and basil, drizzled with balsamic glaze.

Ingredients

  • fresh mozzarella cheese: 4 oz
  • tomato: 1 large, sliced
  • fresh basil leaves: 10 leaves
  • ciabatta bread: 1 loaf
  • balsamic glaze: 1 tbsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
